\[\bm{x}_{i,h+1}^{t,e}=\bm{x}_{i,h}^{t,e}-\gamma\left(\nabla F_{i}(\bm{x}_{i,h}^ {t,e},\,\bm{\xi}_{i,h}^{t,e})+\bm{z}_{i}^{t,e}+\bm{y}_{j}^{t}\right).\] (5)

